        {
            "id": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/long-lasting-ephemera-2.html",
            "url": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/long-lasting-ephemera-2.html",
            "title": "Long-Lasting Ephemera",
            "summary": "Reminiscing about the past brings a mixture of happiness and sadness. There is comfort in the memories, yet also sorrow in knowing those&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n  <p>\n    Reminiscing about the past brings a mixture of happiness and sadness. There is comfort in the memories, yet also sorrow in knowing those moments are gone forever. Distance from my loved ones gave rise to a profound longing for connection. Over time, however, I came to realize that my existence no longer moved continuously within the rhythm of their lives. Years of separation formed an invisible yet unbearable barrier between us.<br>Driven by this bittersweet awareness, I seek to reclaim fleeting moments from the past. Using needle and thread, I stitch into faded photographs to bridge the void between memory and the present. The act of sewing becomes both restoration and meditation—a way of retrieving memories and transforming them into a renewed visual language.\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"2\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/2_Lee_Banana-tree.jpg\" data-size=\"570x1200\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/2_Lee_Banana-tree-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"1200\" width=\"570\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/3_Lee_Candy-vending-machine-copy.jpg\" data-size=\"617x1200\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/3_Lee_Candy-vending-machine-copy-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"1200\" width=\"617\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/DSC00757.JPG\" data-size=\"6000x4000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/DSC00757-thumbnail.JPG\" height=\"480\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/DSC00759.JPG\" data-size=\"6000x4000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/gallery/DSC00759-thumbnail.JPG\" height=\"480\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>\n    \n  </p>",
            "image": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/29/DSC00756.JPG",
