        {
            "id": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/tapestry-2.html",
            "url": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/tapestry-2.html",
            "title": "Together",
            "summary": "It hurts to forget loved ones, or be forgotten by them. This is why I constantly restore fragments of memories. In the middle&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n  <p>\n    It hurts to forget loved ones, or be forgotten by them. This is why I constantly restore fragments of memories. In the middle of weaving, I could walk tho<br>forgotten by them. This is why I<br>constantly restore fragments of<br>memories. In the middle of weaving, I<br>could walk thorough old memories,<br>which have some lost pieces or painful<br>attachments through all little stitches\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"2\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/27/gallery/lee_together-scaled.jpg\" data-size=\"2560x1920\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/27/gallery/lee_together-scaled-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"540\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/27/gallery/lee_together_detail-scaled.jpg\" data-size=\"2560x2042\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/27/gallery/lee_together_detail-scaled-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"574\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
